data.description: This inviting Cape Cod radiates warmth and comfort. As you enter through the front door, the main floor welcomes you with an inviting ambiance, featuring an airy living room where sunlight glistens through large windows. Adjacent, a separate dining room awaits offering seamless flow to the backyard through a convenient door. The well-appointed eat-in kitchen beckons culinary adventures. Nearby, two generously sized bedrooms provide cozy retreats, each with windows that usher in natural light to create tranquil spaces for rest. A full bathroom on this level ensures convenience for all residents. Ascending to the second floor, discover two additional bedrooms, each boasting their own unique character. A second full bathroom upstairs ensures comfort and convenience for all occupants. Descending to the finished basement, a versatile family room awaits, offering the perfect setting for movie nights or game days. A convenient laundry facility simplifies household chores, and a dedicated storage room for convenience. Throughout the home, wood and carpet floors enhancing the overall coziness and charm. An attached garage provides shelter for vehicles, while the fenced backyard offers privacy and security, creating an ideal space for outdoor activities and enjoyment.
